ex:Evidence_Patient_989_lipitor_permanent_joint_damage_988 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.955_988 ;
    ex:sentenceText "i believe that lipitor left me with permanent joint damage and would join any class-action lawsuit relating to this crumby drug lipitor." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_989_lipitor_permanent_joint_damage .

ex:Evidence_Patient_98_norvasc_paranoia_97 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.106_97 ;
    ex:sentenceText "however, at that time - over a month ago - i was only aware of norvasc's side effects and, indeed, when i stopped taking it most of the anxiety and paranoia symptoms disappeared - most, but not all." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_98_norvasc_paranoia .

ex:Evidence_Patient_990_lipitor_tias_989 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.956_989 ;
    ex:sentenceText "when i began taking lipitor i had what the doctors referred to as tia's." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_990_lipitor_tias .

ex:Evidence_Patient_991_lipitor_legs_were_hurting_too_much_990 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.957_990 ;
    ex:sentenceText "i took 5mg day of lipitor for a year but finally quit as my legs were hurting too much." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_991_lipitor_legs_were_hurting_too_much .

ex:Evidence_Patient_992_lipitor_liver_damage_991 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.961_991 ;
    ex:sentenceText "has anyone else out there developed liver damage from lipitor." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_992_lipitor_liver_damage .

ex:Evidence_Patient_993_crestor_mild_pain_992 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.970_992 ;
    ex:sentenceText "presently on crestor one time per week with occasional side effect of mild pain." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_993_crestor_mild_pain .

ex:Evidence_Patient_994_lipitor_cancer_993 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.972_993 ;
    ex:sentenceText "that cancer was diagnosed 6 months after his initial rx for lipitor -- he died 2 months after his initial cancer diagnosis." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_994_lipitor_cancer .

ex:Evidence_Patient_995_lipitor_cancer_994 a ex:Evidence ;
    ex:mentionedInSentence ex:Sentence_LIPITOR.972_994 ;
    ex:sentenceText "i will say that there was no way any doctor could have known this would happen my research showed that lipitor could contribute to this cancer with prior risk factors for it which would have to have been environmental exposure and from what i know of my father's work history experience , but it would help if conventional medicine would listen to patients and their families about experiences that we all are reporting in places such as this." ;
    ex:supportsRelation ex:Relation_Patient_995_lipitor_cancer .

