    ex:sentenceText "fast forward 3 years, he went to doctor for check up he has known coronary disease and was started back on lipitor 20mg. at about 2 months in, he had nausea and sweating occasionally. fast forward 3 years, he went to doctor for check up he has known coronary disease and was started back on lipitor 20mg. at about 2 months in, he had nausea and sweating occasionally. we thought it was the toprol at first due to low bp and pulse also."^^xsd:string .

