    ex:sentenceText "about a week ago, in the middle of the night after taking my usual lipitor dose, while making my nightly trip to the toilet, a severe muscle back cramp almost sent me to the floor. since i had done nothing recently to cause a cramp or spasm, and realizing that in the past, the back aches usually were the worst in the morning but got better during the day and best at night just before my lipitor dose, i suspected lipitor. since i had done nothing recently to cause a cramp or spasm, and realizing that in the past, the back aches usually were the worst in the morning but got better during the day and best at night just before my lipitor dose, i suspected lipitor. since i had done nothing recently to cause a cramp or spasm, and realizing that in the past, the back aches usually were the worst in the morning but got better during the day and best at night just before my lipitor dose, i suspected lipitor."^^xsd:string .

