    ex:mentionsDrug ex:Drug_lipitor,
        ex:Drug_liptor ;
    ex:postID "LIPITOR.381" ;
    ex:sentenceText "never had any problems walking, after liptor had severe muscle spasms in my legs, thigh area. had difficulty reaching seat and unable to walk, waited for pain to subside before i could continue, off lipitor now. had difficulty reaching seat and unable to walk, waited for pain to subside before i could continue, off lipitor now. had difficulty reaching seat and unable to walk, waited for pain to subside before i could continue, off lipitor now. 6 months post lipitor i am still experiencing periodic muscle pain and i wonder will i ever totally get back to the way i used to be. would be grateful for any advice. i am thankful to be rid of the awful muscle spasms i experienced whilst taking lipitor and would advise people to think very carefully before taking this drug."^^xsd:string .

