    ex:postID "LIPITOR.468" ;
    ex:sentenceText "started on lipitor about 6 months ago. 2-3 weeks ago i went to md with sore neck arms especially left feeling of breathlessness and anxiety, feeling like something was going to happen. started on lipitor about 6 months ago. 2-3 weeks ago i went to md with sore neck arms especially left feeling of breathlessness and anxiety, feeling like something was going to happen. started on lipitor about 6 months ago. 2-3 weeks ago i went to md with sore neck arms especially left feeling of breathlessness and anxiety, feeling like something was going to happen. started on lipitor about 6 months ago. 2-3 weeks ago i went to md with sore neck arms especially left feeling of breathlessness and anxiety, feeling like something was going to happen. md told me i was depressed and said lipitor was not the problem. i immediately stopped taking lipitor a day ago and am experiencing weakness in both arms especially left."^^xsd:string .

