        ex:Drug_steroid_nasal_sprays ;
    ex:postID "LIPITOR.59" ;
    ex:sentenceText "over the years, i had previously been prescribed steroid nasal sprays, allegra even though tests showed no allergies , nexium, cough medicine, sinus irrigation, and various sleeping pills to deal with what i now know was my reaction to statins. over the years, i had previously been prescribed steroid nasal sprays, allegra even though tests showed no allergies , nexium, cough medicine, sinus irrigation, and various sleeping pills to deal with what i now know was my reaction to statins. over the years, i had previously been prescribed steroid nasal sprays, allegra even though tests showed no allergies , nexium, cough medicine, sinus irrigation, and various sleeping pills to deal with what i now know was my reaction to statins. over the years, i had previously been prescribed steroid nasal sprays, allegra even though tests showed no allergies , nexium, cough medicine, sinus irrigation, and various sleeping pills to deal with what i now know was my reaction to statins. now 12 days post-lipitor, the hot flashes and night sweats are gone entirely. now 12 days post-lipitor, the hot flashes and night sweats are gone entirely."^^xsd:string .

