ull range of motion took a year to recover tremor disappeared vision in eye awaiting cataract surgery improved to pre-mevacor level my eye surgeon said that he had seen existing cataracts made more severe by statins in other patients as well noticed distinct improvement mental function in two weeks."^^xsd:string .

