    ex:postID "LIPITOR.196" ;
    ex:sentenceText "after taking lipitor for 1 week, my resting pulse jumped to between 100 and 105, and i started experiencing dizziness, lack of energy tireness , and unexplained sweating. after taking lipitor for 1 week, my resting pulse jumped to between 100 and 105, and i started experiencing dizziness, lack of energy tireness , and unexplained sweating. after taking lipitor for 1 week, my resting pulse jumped to between 100 and 105, and i started experiencing dizziness, lack of energy tireness , and unexplained sweating. after taking lipitor for 1 week, my resting pulse jumped to between 100 and 105, and i started experiencing dizziness, lack of energy tireness , and unexplained sweating. other symptoms which started occurring after a few days of lipiltor include sever leg muscle pain, swelling of the lower legs and feet, and even more sudden and pronounced sweating at random, unexplained times. other symptoms which started occurring after a few days of lipiltor include sever leg muscle pain, swelling of the lower legs and feet, and even more sudden and pronounced sweating at random, unexplained times. other symptoms which started occurring after a few days of lipiltor include sever leg muscle pain, swelling of the lower legs and feet, and even more sudden and pronounced sweating at random, unexplained times."^^xsd:string .

