    ex:mentionsDrug ex:Drug_coq10,
        ex:Drug_statins ;
    ex:postID "LIPITOR.365" ;
    ex:sentenceText "for all of you who now have extremely low ldl and a bad case of joint pain to the extent that it is very arthritic or having bad muscle cramps that you never got prior to the drug, it is from the statins. for all of you who now have extremely low ldl and a bad case of joint pain to the extent that it is very arthritic or having bad muscle cramps that you never got prior to the drug, it is from the statins. if you do some research on the internet, you will find that all these statins make no claims nor have studies shown them to reduce heart attacks, but they cause muscle problems i.e. your heart, this is based on the fact that they put younger and younger people on these drugs and. if you do some research on the internet, you will find that all these statins make no claims nor have studies shown them to reduce heart attacks, but they cause muscle problems i.e. your heart, this is based on the fact that they put younger and younger people on these drugs and. and just because your test come back and show your liver functions are fine and don't show any broken down muscle toxins in the blood doesn't mean the lack of coq10 isn't breaking down and damaging your muscles very slowly. and i had severe arthritis symptoms in knees and hip joints never had this in my life before statins and bad muscle cramps also never got those until statins . and i had severe arthritis symptoms in knees and hip joints never had this in my life before statins and bad muscle cramps also never got those until statins ."^^xsd:string .

