        ex:Drug_zocor ;
    ex:postID "LIPITOR.327" ;
    ex:sentenceText "i started on zocor and changed to lipitor after 1 year because of balance problems. i started on zocor and changed to lipitor after 1 year because of balance problems. after a couple of years i began to experience balance problems and joint pain, but the doctor did not think that lipitor was causing the problems. after a couple of years i began to experience balance problems and joint pain, but the doctor did not think that lipitor was causing the problems. he prescribed 40 milligrams of lipitor for several years and eventually added gemfibrosil, and niacin because of high triglycerides. he prescribed 40 milligrams of lipitor for several years and eventually added gemfibrosil, and niacin because of high triglycerides. he prescribed 40 milligrams of lipitor for several years and eventually added gemfibrosil, and niacin because of high triglycerides. the doctors took me off the lipitor after the kidney readings became so high."^^xsd:string .

