    ex:postID "LIPITOR.359" ;
    ex:sentenceText "i used to take provachol sp? but i found it caused extreme bloating. as far as side effects are concerned, i find that lipitor also causes bloating and a great deal of gas build up although not as badly as my previous medication. as far as side effects are concerned, i find that lipitor also causes bloating and a great deal of gas build up although not as badly as my previous medication. i have begun to take charge of fighting back against the side effects and have been taking multivitamins, b complex, coq10, and gasx for bloating. i have begun to take charge of fighting back against the side effects and have been taking multivitamins, b complex, coq10, and gasx for bloating. i have begun to take charge of fighting back against the side effects and have been taking multivitamins, b complex, coq10, and gasx for bloating. he took tums to alliviate stomach upsets and also cut his lipitor dose in half. he took tums to alliviate stomach upsets and also cut his lipitor dose in half."^^xsd:string .

