    ex:postID "LIPITOR.422" ;
    ex:sentenceText "i was ok at first and it did lower my cholesterol but a was feeling tired a lot but didn't make any connection to lipitor. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. after taking lipitor 20mg for 3 years the side effects for the last few months are feeling tired all the time, sore weak muscles in left arm and leg, short term memory loss, less patience, loose temper faster, hair loss, comments from friends that i have aged a lot in the last 2 years. i went to the doctor 11-26-04 and told him that i quit lipitor 11-20-04 and already feel a lot better except for the very sore neck."^^xsd:string .

